thread.title: Elizabeth Kibler

author: Elizabeth Kibler
title: Elizabeth Kibler
text: This was my first time using Maxback and I'm really impressed! The whole process went very smoothly and it was really quick! I got my shipping label on January 23rd, shipped it the 24th and the money was available to me on Paypal on January 28th. I was also given a few dollars more than my original Quote: ! I had a great experience overall and will definitely use this website again!
